  Projects 
Title Blended learning platform for school students 
Objective To make a common platform for learning and student 
management with AI, 3D models 
Description This platform consists of virtual reverse engineering of 
concepts and visualizing them in 3D interactive models and an 
evaluative AI chatbot to ensure peer and peer learning. 
 
 
Title Sign language to Text translator  
Objective To help mute people to communicate easily. 
Description The system consists of glove with implanted flex and gyro-
accelerometer sensor which converts hand gestures into digital 
output. A microcontroller is interfaced to convert digital 
signals into text and display in a OLED display. 
 
Title Pepper harvesting system using image processing   
Objective To ensure the safety of Pepper harvesters, precise segregation 
and quality harvests and increase the rate of harvesting. 
Description This system consists of an image processing algorithm to 
segregate green and red peppers and a precise control system for 
linear actuation mounted on a pole like structure to make it 
portable. 
 
Title Realtime medical supply chain monitoring system (Vaccines) 
Objective To ensure the safety and integrity of vaccines during 
transportation by monitoring temperature, humidity and 
location. 
Description This system utilizes temperature, humidity sensors and GPS 
tracker within containers to monitor conditions and location. If 
temperature or humidity deviates, alerts are sent with precise 
data and GPS coordinates, ensuring supply integrity and patient 
safety. Data logging is also done for feature uses.
